  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink264-kilavi">varaiyātu vantoḻukum talaimakaṉaip pakaṟkuṟikkaṇ etirppaṭṭut tōḻi varaivukaṭāyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">The confidante, urging marriage, encountering the hero who kept coming without marrying, at the daytime tryst.    
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink264">
<l>iḷampiṟai yaṉṉa kōṭṭa kēḻal</l>
<l>kaḷaṅkaṉi yaṉṉa peṇpāṟ puṇaru</l>
<l>mayantikaḻ cilampa kaṇṭikum</l>
<l>pacantaṉa mātōnī nayantōḷ kaṇṇē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>We have seen that the eyes</l>
        <l>of the woman you longed for have grown pale,</l>
        
        <l rend="space indent">O man from the mountain slope glittering with water,</l>
        <l rend="indent">where boars, with tusks like the young crescent moon,</l>
        <l rend="indent">unite with their females,</l>
        <l rend="indent">which are like the ripe kaḷam fruit.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
